{
  "page": "Undying Ones",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Undying Ones</b> are the chief <a href=\"/index.php/Warlocks\" title=\"Warlocks\">warlocks</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafhouse_of_the_undying.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafhouse_of_the_undying.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> dwelling in a chamber deep in the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Undying\" title=\"House of the Undying\">House of the Undying</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undying_Ones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Undying Ones present themselves as beautiful wizards at the prime of their lives and power, with some wearing sumptuous robes, elaborate armor, or tall pointed hats. They include gown-clad women.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> In actuality, however, the Undying Ones are ancient and withered. Through their drinking of the <a href=\"/index.php/Shade_of_the_evening\" title=\"Shade of the evening\">shade of the evening</a>, their flesh, nails, and even the whites of their eyes have turned shades of blue and violet-blue.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undying_Ones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undying_Ones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg/350px-House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg/525px-House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg/700px-House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_of_Dust_MarcSimonetti.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Undying Ones attack <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, by Marc Simonetti ©</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Pyat_Pree\" title=\"Pyat Pree\">Pyat Pree</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Warlocks\" title=\"Warlocks\">warlocks</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, informs <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> that he will ask the Undying Ones to grant her an audience.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> After being rejected by the <a href=\"/index.php/Pureborn\" title=\"Pureborn\">Pureborn</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Daenerys decides to meet the Undying Ones.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In a great hall within the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Undying\" title=\"House of the Undying\">House of the Undying</a>, Daenerys finds a splendor of wizards who offer her knowledge and magic weapons. <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a>, one of Daenerys's <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>, points her to another door, however, so she abandons these wizards who call on her with sweet voices.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In a gloomy chamber, Daenerys finds a blue and rotting human heart floating above a stone table, and in the darkness she perceives the true Undying Ones. Although they do not move and do not breathe, Daenerys hears them whisper. The Undying Ones show Daenerys a number of <a href=\"/index.php/Visions\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Visions\">visions</a> of past and future events, but as they do so they attack her and attempt to drain her life. Drogon rescues Daenerys, however, burning the Undying Ones with <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonflame\" title=\"Dragonflame\">dragonflame</a> and ripping apart the dark heart. Pyat Pree tries to attack Daenerys when she escapes from the building, but he is stopped by <a href=\"/index.php/Jhogo\" title=\"Jhogo\">Jhogo</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rakharo\" title=\"Rakharo\">Rakharo</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undying_Ones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>According to <a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a>, the Undying are all dead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undying_Ones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>When you come to the chamber of the Undying, be patient. Our little lives are no more than a flicker of a moth's wing to them. Listen well, and write each word upon your heart.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Pyat_Pree\" title=\"Pyat Pree\">Pyat Pree</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Woman</b>: Long have we awaited you.<br />\n</p><p><b>King</b>: We knew you were to come to us. A thousand years ago we knew, and have been waiting all this time. We sent <a href=\"/index.php/Red_comet\" title=\"Red comet\">the comet</a> to show you the way.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Warrior</b>: We have knowledge to share with you, and <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">magic</a> weapons to arm you with. You have passed every trial. Now come and sit with us, and all your questions shall be answered.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Three of the Undying Ones to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>None of them are breathing, and they do not move, and those eyes see nothing. Could it be that the Undying Ones were dead?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a> saved me when they would have drained my life from me. Drogon burned them all.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undying_Ones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Since <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> has long been a fan of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doctor_Strange\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Doctor Strange\">Doctor Strange</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> the Undying Ones of Qarth may be a homage by Martin to <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Undying_Ones\">demons of the same name</a> who have fought Strange and the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Defenders_(comics)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Defenders (comics)\">Defenders</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Undying_Ones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafhouse_of_the_undying.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafhouse_of_the_undying.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, House of the Undying.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\">2.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\">2.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\">2.7</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_48\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 48\">Chapter 48</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 40\">Chapter 40</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">DigitalSpy.com: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.digitalspy.com/comics/a407360/game-of-thrones-george-rr-martin-would-write-doctor-strange/\">Game of Thrones' George RR Martin would write 'Doctor Strange'</a>, 21 September 2012</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403104243\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.039 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.040 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1403/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9200/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6330/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1587/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 5063/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   26.467      1 -total\n 79.76%   21.110     13 Template:Ref\n 51.78%   13.704     13 Template:Ref/core\n 25.91%    6.857      4 Template:Quote\n 11.46%    3.032      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:9348-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403104243 and revision id 275312\n -->\n",
